Version 1alpha5 - internally released 2013-09-17
* added ID column (default for sorting)
* removed powered by link

Version 1alpha4 - internally released 2012-11-19
* implemented resetting of votes from back-end

Version 1alpha3 - internally released 2012-07-04
* made sorting and filtering case insensitive (but not yet locale aware)
* added list view signals, if current user has already voted

Version 1alpha2 - internally released 2012-06-13
* changed: states have classes instead of fixed colors (inspired by svasti)
* changed: default column widths and font-size larger (suggested by svasti)
* added possibility to vote (suggested by svasti)

Version 1alpha1 - internally released 2012-06-10
* fixed bug: empty link field was displayed (reported by svasti)
* fixed bug: newlines were not properly escaped in JSON response
* fixed bug: list refresh was done asynchronously
* added copyright and license information
* added basic back-end
* added i18n
* added config options folder_data and col_widths
* added file locking and some error handling
* cleaned up code

Version 1dev1 - internally released 2012-06-06
* initial release
